Install the following modules in this folder:

git clone https://github.com/shbatm/MMM-KeyBindings

git clone https://github.com/shbatm/MMM-Carousel

git clone https://github.com/uxigene/MMM-QRCode
cd MMM-QRCode
npm install

git clone https://github.com/SalekurPolas/MMM-Pinfo
cd MMM-Pinfo
npm install